                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[15px] text-[#5f3647]">
                  <li><strong>Remuneration:</strong> <%= euro_display(@mission.compensation_summary.presence || "90 000€ - 120 000€") %></li>
                  <li><strong>Voiture de fonction:</strong> Oui</li>
                  <li><strong>13eme mois:</strong> Inclus</li>
                  <li><strong>Tickets restaurants:</strong> Oui</li>
                  <li><strong>Mutuelle:</strong> Premium</li>
                  <li><strong>Bonus:</strong> Variable annuel selon performance</li>
                </ul>
              </article>

              <article class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-[#efdbe4] bg-white/80 p-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#5b2633]">Deroulee du recrutement</h4>
                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[15px] text-[#5f3647]">
                  <li><strong>Nombre d entretiens:</strong> 3</li>
                  <li><strong>1er entretien:</strong> Echange RH avec RIVYR</li>
                  <li><strong>2eme entretien:</strong> Rencontre avec le manager operationnel</li>
                  <li><strong>3eme entretien:</strong> Entretien final avec la direction</li>
                  <li><strong>Prise de references:</strong> A l issue du dernier entretien</li>
                  <li><strong>Decision finale:</strong> Sous 72h apres le dernier echange</li>
                </ul>
              </article>

              <% if mission_assigned %>
                <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-[#5b2633]">Documents utiles</h4>
                <div class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[14px] text-[#5f3647]">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[#ead2dc] px-3 py-2">
                    <span>Job description complete</span>
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                      <span class="relative inline-flex cursor-help items-center" onmouseenter="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.remove('hidden')" onmouseleave="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.add('hidden')">
                        <span class="btn btn-xs pointer-events-none rounded-full border-[#e7d7de] bg-[#f7f2f5] text-[#c4aab4]" title="Disponible apres affectation">
                          <i class="fa-solid fa-video"></i>
                        </span>
                        <span class="document-lock-help pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-full z-40 mt-2 hidden w-56 rounded-xl border border-[#f2ddd6] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs text-[#6f332b] shadow-lg">Disponible apres affectation</span>
                      </span>
                      <span class="relative inline-flex cursor-help items-center" onmouseenter="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.remove('hidden')" onmouseleave="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.add('hidden')">
                        <span class="btn btn-xs pointer-events-none rounded-full border-[#e7d7de] bg-[#f7f2f5] text-[#c4aab4]" title="Disponible apres affectation">
                          <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                        </span>
                        <span class="document-lock-help pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-full z-40 mt-2 hidden w-56 rounded-xl border border-[#f2ddd6] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs text-[#6f332b] shadow-lg">Disponible apres affectation</span>
                      </span>
                    </span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[#ead2dc] px-3 py-2">
                    <div class="min-w-0">
                      <span class="<%= assigned_and_accepted ? 'text-[#5f3647]' : 'text-[#9a7582]' %>">Presentation entreprise</span>
                    </div>
                    <% if assigned_and_accepted %>
                      <button type="button" class="btn btn-xs rounded-full border-[#dfbcc9] bg-[#fff5f8] text-[#8b4452] hover:bg-[#fdeef3]" title="Presentation entreprise" onclick="document.getElementById('company_modal').showModal()">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                      </button>
                    <% else %>
                      <span class="relative inline-flex cursor-help items-center" onmouseenter="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.remove('hidden')" onmouseleave="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.add('hidden')">
                        <span class="btn btn-xs pointer-events-none rounded-full border-[#e7d7de] bg-[#f7f2f5] text-[#c4aab4]" title="Disponible apres affectation">
                          <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                        </span>
                        <span class="document-lock-help pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-full z-40 mt-2 hidden w-56 rounded-xl border border-[#f2ddd6] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs text-[#6f332b] shadow-lg">Disponible apres affectation</span>
                      </span>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 rounded-xl border border-[#ead2dc] px-3 py-2">
                    <div class="min-w-0 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="<%= assigned_and_accepted ? 'text-[#5f3647]' : 'text-[#9a7582]' %>">Contrat</span>
                      <span class="relative inline-flex cursor-help items-center" onmouseenter="this.querySelector('.signature-status-help').classList.remove('hidden')" onmouseleave="this.querySelector('.signature-status-help').classList.add('hidden')">
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold <%= contract_status[:classes] %>"><%= contract_status[:label] %></span>
                        <span class="signature-status-help pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-full z-40 mt-2 hidden w-72 rounded-xl border border-[#f2ddd6] bg-white px-3 py-3 text-left shadow-lg">
                          <span class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#9a5a68]">Etapes de signature</span>
                          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#5f3647]">
                            <% signature_steps.each_with_index do |step, idx| %>
                              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="<%= step[:done] ? 'border-[#97c6a3] bg-[#edf8f0] text-[#2f6b3c]' : 'border-[#e7d7de] bg-[#f7f2f5] text-[#b49aa4]' %> flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full border text-[10px] font-semibold"><%= idx + 1 %></span>
                                <span class="<%= idx == signature_current_index ? 'font-semibold text-[#4c1f2a]' : 'text-[#6f4a58]' %>"><%= step[:label] %></span>
                              </li>
                          <% end %>
                        </ul>
                      </span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                    <% if assigned_and_accepted %>
                      <%= link_to mission_path(@mission), class: "btn btn-xs rounded-full border-[#dfbcc9] bg-[#fff5f8] text-[#8b4452] hover:bg-[#fdeef3]", title: "Contrat" do %>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                      <% end %>
                    <% else %>
                      <span class="relative inline-flex cursor-help items-center" onmouseenter="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.remove('hidden')" onmouseleave="this.querySelector('.document-lock-help').classList.add('hidden')">
                        <span class="btn btn-xs pointer-events-none rounded-full border-[#e7d7de] bg-[#f7f2f5] text-[#c4aab4]" title="Disponible apres affectation">
                          <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                        </span>
                        <span class="document-lock-help pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-full z-40 mt-2 hidden w-56 rounded-xl border border-[#f2ddd6] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-left text-xs text-[#6f332b] shadow-lg">Disponible apres affectation</span>
                      </span>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </article>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <% if policy(@mission).edit? %>
        <%= link_to "Modifier", edit_mission_path(@mission), class: "btn border-[#dfbcc9] bg-[#fff2f7] text-[#7a3a49] hover:bg-[#fce7ef]" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<dialog id="rivyr_score_modal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-box max-w-md rounded-2xl border border-[#ead5ce] bg-white">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#6f332b]">Indice mission RIVYR : <%= rivyr_index %>/10</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#6b3f4f]">Cet indice combine 4 dimensions pour aider le freelance a decider vite :</p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-[#5e3742]">
      <li><strong>Qualite client:</strong> <%= quality_score %>/10</li>
      <li><strong>Niveau de difficulte:</strong> <%= difficulty_score %>/10</li>
      <li><strong>Attractivite du poste:</strong> <%= attractiveness_score %>/10</li>
      <li><strong>Probabilite de closing:</strong> <%= closing_score %>/10</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-[#8d5f6b]">Objectif: t aider a trancher en moins de 60 secondes.</p>
    <div class="modal-action">
      <form method="dialog"><button class="btn btn-sm">Fermer</button></form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <form method="dialog" class="modal-backdrop"><button>close</button></form>
</dialog>

<dialog id="commission_breakdown_modal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-box max-w-lg rounded-2xl border border-[#ead5ce] bg-white">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#6f332b]">Detail du calcul de commission</h3>
    <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-sm text-[#5f3647]">
      <p><strong>Remuneration brute moyenne:</strong> <%= format_amount(fee_breakdown[:salary_average]) %>€</p>
      <p><strong>Honoraires RIVYR:</strong> <%= format_amount(fee_breakdown[:salary_average]) %> x <%= (fee_breakdown[:contract_rate] * 100).round %>% = <%= format_amount(fee_breakdown[:gross_fee]) %>€</p>
      <p><strong>Part freelance:</strong> <%= format_amount(fee_breakdown[:gross_fee]) %> x <%= (fee_breakdown[:freelance_rate] * 100).round %>% = <%= format_amount(fee_breakdown[:fee_amount]) %>€</p>
      <p class="rounded-xl border border-[#efdbe4] bg-[#fff8fb] px-3 py-2 text-[#6f4a58]">
        Formule appliquee: remuneration brute moyenne x honoraires RIVYR x part freelance.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-action">
      <form method="dialog"><button class="btn btn-sm">Fermer</button></form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <form method="dialog" class="modal-backdrop"><button>close</button></form>
</dialog>

